{"tid":1675016,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際戰線] 叫D外國人一齊學中文!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-10-25T14:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T15:28:34.000Z","uid":220045,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e2399c4f164056aa365894ec8ada82987f4bf0dd","tid":1675016,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"大家都知呢幾個月黎中文好多<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">新字</span></span><br />\n例如係以下4個:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T6G3ocb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT6G3ocb.jpg&h=ee3af494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jBZXsDR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjBZXsDR.jpg&h=4bb7d3ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iH6VYLw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiH6VYLw.jpg&h=2096c7ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eeAPiLx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeeAPiLx.jpg&h=f7854fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人覺得呢D字其實真係好有<span style=\"color: pink;\">時代意義</span><br />\n背後亦有好多意思, 一路望個畫面真係出哂黎<br />\n而字呢d野其實係好<span style=\"color: violet;\">iconic同symbolic</span>, 容易令人<span style=\"color: purple;\">印象深刻、容易傳播</span><br />\n我地又可以藉住呢幾個字<span style=\"color: green;\">好簡單咁就講到比人知香港既基本情況</span><br />\n同時外國人近呢10年開始興起左<span style=\"color: red;\">學中文既潮流</span><br />\n所以我就係度唸<br />\n如果將呢D字<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>推上國際</strong></span></span>, 叫外國人學同從中知道更多香港發生咩事<br />\n會唔會算係有gimmick同吸引, 又可以當係國際文宣, 保持國際關注<br />\n我唸到有兩個方法:<br />\n1. 舊酒新瓶 - 整一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">challenge</span></span>鼓勵人學呢D字<br />\n2. 搵方法<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">令國際字典 eg. Oxford, Cambridge 將呢D字錄入</span></span><br />\n第二個方法做既途徑我暫時淨係搵到可以直接contact D字典, 但唔知人地咁樣會唔會收<br />\n<br />\n以上都只係brainstorm, 大家有咩意見歡迎提出, 一齊集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS. 其實2日前已經出過一次Post, 但好多意見都集中係上字典呢個方法唔work, <span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">想知多D有冇意見比到整challenge果個方法</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b09b8560c7e4995e8d054e40bd00525be3efe3e","tid":1675016,"uid":19984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"我宣布，十點鐘鳩嗌，正式回歸！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1674226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1674226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1MzDWAt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1MzDWAt.jpg&h=8b11f628&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35a8bef55d233a6dbc043fc06d28a1036d940d1c","tid":1675016,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99d321e874d7024aadbf3d5ec88b11a7491539b8","tid":1675016,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:28:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">10月26日</span></strong></span><br />\n「醫民同行. 共抗警暴」<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">遮打集會1800</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hf293f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhf293f3.jpg&h=48e668cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">10月27日</span></span></strong><br />\n「追究警暴  連繫穆斯林<br />\n守護民眾  與記者同行」<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>梳士巴利花園 1500</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvA0quw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFv